etail:"Their main side. Dorito will be under-defended — send a player there.",insight_side_vuln_text:(e,t)=>`Loses points when attacked through ${e} — ${t}% of losses`,insight_side_vuln_detail:e=>`We win ${e}% when we attack that side. Keep pressuring there.`,insight_center_text:e=>`Controls center in ${e}% of points`,insight_center_detail:"They dominate center — limit crossfires and respect the mid player.",insight_uncovered_text:e=>`They don't shoot toward ${e} during obstacle play`,insight_uncovered_detail:e=>`A player entering through ${e} will meet minimal resistance.`,insight_player_strong_text:e=>`Key player makes a big difference (+${e}% win rate when playing)`,insight_player_strong_detail:(e,t,n)=>`With them: ${e}% wins. Without: ${t}% (${n} pts).`,insight_player_weak_text:e=>`One player drags the team (${e}%)`,insight_player_weak_detail:(e,t,n)=>`With them: ${e}% wins vs ${t}% without (${n} pts).`,insight_late_break_text:e=>`Secondary push after break — ${e}% of points`,insight_late_break_detail:"They send a player a moment after the buzzer. Hold lanes active for a few seconds.",insight_predictable_text:e=>`Predictable — same setup in ${e}% of points`,insight_predictable_detail:(e,t,n)=>`${e} of ${t} points: ${n}. Prep a specific counter.`,insight_unpredictable_text:e=>`Unpredictable — ${e} different break setups`,insight_unpredictable_detail:e=>`No setup dominates (max ${e}%). Play solid fundamentals, not one counter.`,formation_on_dorito:e=>`${e} on dorito`,formation_on_snake:e=>`${e} on snake`,formation_in_center:e=>`${e} in center`,counter_fifty_action:e=>`Hold lanes on the ${e} side`,counter_fifty_detail:e=>`They push the fifty aggressively via ${e}. Set a player to hold the lane and kill the runner before they reach the fifty.`,counter_pocket_action:"Survive the break — read their lanes",counter_pocket_detail:"They have 4+ players shooting from the base. Don't run through paint — wait for a reload or quiet moment, then attack the open tape.",counter_